info.title: Object Dependency
info.description: Object dependencies are used to set and maintain rules in variant configuration. An object dependency can be assigned to BOM items, task list items, characteristics, characteristic values and configuration profiles. All actions support change numbers.

x-sap-shortText: Create, read, update and delete basic data, language-specific descriptions and source codes of an object dependency on a specific date with this synchronous inbound service
